oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Fieldnotes on Lincoln Street Church of Christ. Notes document the location of the church and provide a brief architectural description of the building.

Located in Alamo, Tennessee, Lincoln Street Church of Christ is a rural African American church. The current building, described as a "very good circa 1950 building," sits across the street from the First Baptist Church.
